y 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-function.odbc-num-rows-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    <p class="para">    Using <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">odbc_num_rows()</strong></span> to determine the number of rows    available after a SELECT will return -1 with many drivers.   </p>  </p></blockquote> </div></div>
