eter" style="color:#3A95FF">dsn</span>,   <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">user</span>, <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">password</span>   combination (via <span class="function">{@link odbc_connect()}</span> and   <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">odbc_pconnect()</strong></span>) can reuse the persistent   connection.  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.odbc-pconnect-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <span>   See <span class="function">{@link odbc_connect()}</span> for details.  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.odbc-pconnect-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns an ODBC connection,  或者在失败时返回 <strong><span>false</span></strong>.   error.  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-function.odbc-pconnect-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    <span class="simpara">    Persistent connections have no effect if PHP is used as a CGI    program.   </span>  </p></blockquote> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.odbc-pconnect-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_connect()} - Connect to a datasource</span></li>    <li class="member"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/features.persistent-connections.php" class="link">Persistent Database Connections</a></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
