ed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.odbc-primarykeys-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <div class="example" id="example-3038">   <p><strong>示例 #1 List primary Keys of a Column</strong></p>   <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$conn </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">odbc_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$dsn</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$user</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pass</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$primarykeys </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">odbc_primarykeys</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'TutorialDB'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'dbo'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'TEST'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />while ((</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$row </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">odbc_fetch_array</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$primarykeys</span><span style="color: #007700">))) {<br />    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">print_r</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$row</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />    break; </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// further rows omitted for brevity<br /></span><span style="color: #007700">}<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></span></div>   </div>   <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例的输出类似于：</p></div>   <div class="example-contents screen" style="color:AFB1B3;background:black;padding-left:5px;"><div class="cdata"><span>Array<br>(<br>    [TABLE_CAT] =&gt; TutorialDB<br>    [TABLE_SCHEM] =&gt; dbo<br>    [TABLE_NAME] =&gt; TEST<br>    [COLUMN_NAME] =&gt; id<br>    [KEY_SEQ] =&gt; 1<br>    [PK_NAME] =&gt; PK__TEST__3213E83FE141F843<br>)<br></span></div>   </div>  </div> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.odbc-primarykeys-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_tables()} - Get the list of table names stored in a specific data source</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_foreignkeys()} - Retrieves a list of foreign keys</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
